<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-2255] ColumnFamilyOutputFormat drops mutations when batches fill up.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2255</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;queue.poll() takes a mutation,&lt;br/&gt;
but then the batch is already full,&lt;br/&gt;
so the while loop exits, ant the mutation we just got is dropped.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12499973">CASSANDRA-2255</key>
