    fix Hadoop ColumnFamilyOutputFormat droppingof mutations&lt;br/&gt;
patch by Eldon Stegall and Jeremy Hanna; reviewed by jbellis for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2255&quot; title=&quot;ColumnFamilyOutputFormat drops mutations when batches fill up.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-2255&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-2255&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
